 spremljenija činiti dobro.

622
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:47,960
 Ako se to ne događa

623
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:48,260
 s molitva,

624
00:31:48,260 --> 00:31:48,980
 nešto nije u redu.

625
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:51,180
 Na ovom razini ja govorim,

626
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:51,880
 Bog me čuje,

627
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,980
 molitva se rađa iz srca.

628
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:55,720
 Jer se rađa iz srca,

629
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:56,880
 ulazi u Božje srce

630
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:57,780
 i Bog je čuje.

631
00:31:57,780 --> 00:32:00,000
 I ta molitva postaje kanal,

632
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:02,120
 postaje kanal po kojem sadržaj

633
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:03,400
 iz Božje srca se pretaču

634
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,160
 u moje srce.

635
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:06,140
 Ali postoji još dublja molitva.

636
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:08,240
 Bog govori, ja čujem.

637
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:10,000
 Mi smo zaboravili šutjeti.

638
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,300
 Nas previše riječi,

639
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:16,160
 banjska tišina,

640
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,100
 nutrenja sabranost

641
00:32:17,100 --> 00:32:18,920
 su dva važna preduvjeta

642
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:19,580
 za molitvu.

643
00:32:19,580 --> 00:32:21,380
 Molitva je u biti,

644
00:32:21,380 --> 00:32:22,900
 ispravna molitva ima

645
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:25,900
 dva nužna uvjeta,

646
00:32:25,900 --> 00:32:27,640
 a to je pozornost

647
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,660
 i pobožnost.

648
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:30,940
 Ako nema toga,

649
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:32,340
 pobožnost je ništa drugo

650
00:32:32,340 --> 00:32:32,920
 nego ljubav prema

651
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:33,700
 gospodinu Bogu.

652
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:35,380
 Ako nema ove sabranosti,

653
00:32:35,380 --> 00:32:37,880
 ako nema ovog napora

654
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:39,640
 da ja uđem u dijalog,

655
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:41,360
 u razgovor s gospodinom Bogom,

656
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,240
 nema molitve,

657
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,420
 postaje samo na klapanje.

658
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:44,780
 Dakle,

659
00:32:44,780 --> 00:32:47,400
 kad dođem do stupnja

660
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,940
 da mi je tišina važna,

661
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,340
 da se povlačem u sebe,

662
00:32:50,340 --> 00:32:52,920
 tada ću ja uspijeti čuti

663
00:32:52,920 --> 00:32:54,640
 što Bog govori crkvi.

664
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,500
 Odnosno u mom srcu.

665
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,520
 Matamo negdje u knjize utkrivenja,

666
00:32:57,520 --> 00:32:59,200
 duh govori crkvama,

667
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,820
 duh govori crkvu,

668
00:33:00,820 --> 00:33:01,520
 Efezu si miri.

669
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:02,940
 Duh govori meni,

670
00:33:02,940 --> 00:33:03,540
 mojoj crkvi,

671
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:04,180
 mom srcu.

672
00:33:04,180 --> 00:33:05,700
 Ali trebam doći do toga

673
00:33:05,700 --> 00:33:07,480
 da ja čujem što duh poručuje.

674
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:09,420
 Jer duh u meni progovara.

675
00:33:10,020 --> 00:33:12,740
 duh mi otkriva volju očevu

676
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:14,260
 i daj bi snagu da je izvršim.

677
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:16,260
 Ali moram se nauči šutjeti.

678
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:18,960
 Moram nauči se povlačiti u svoju,

679
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:19,420
 kaže Isus,

680
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,860
 povući se u svoju sobu.

681
00:33:20,860 --> 00:33:22,640
 To može bih fizička soba,

682
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:23,980
 ali češće je soba svog srca.

683
00:33:23,980 --> 00:33:25,440
 Povući se u svoju nutrinu,

684
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:28,100
 tu osluškuj što duh poručuje crkvi.

685
00:33:28,100 --> 00:33:29,440
 Što duh poručuje ti.

686
00:33:29,700 --> 00:33:31,080
 Treba puno rada na sebi,

687
00:33:31,080 --> 00:33:32,820
 puno,

688
00:33:32,820 --> 00:33:35,520
 puno, puno truda

689
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,460
 da se osvoji ta sabranu,

690
00:33:37,460 --> 00:33:38,300
 da se sačuva

691
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:39,760
 i da omogućim duhu

692
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:41,060
 da progovori mom srcu.

693
00:33:41,060 --> 00:33:42,420
 Na još dobljoj razini,

694
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:43,240
 četvrtoj razini,

695
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:44,700
 Bog govori

696
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:46,180
 i Bog sluša.

697
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:48,020
 To je već mistična molitva.

698
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:49,880
 Kad osoba doživljava

699
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:50,760
 da se udijeluje u životu

700
00:33:50,760 --> 00:33:51,700
 predstavu trojstva,

701
00:33:52,100 --> 00:33:54,040
 da je otac izgovara u sinu,

702
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:55,380
 ti si moj dijete ljubljeno,

703
00:33:55,380 --> 00:33:56,660
 a ja, moj duh,

704
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:58,460
 sa Isom Kristom u duhu svetom

705
00:33:58,460 --> 00:33:58,820
 dogovara,

706
00:33:58,820 --> 00:33:59,800
 Abba, oče,

707
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:01,100
 nek se vrši tvoja volja.

708
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:03,120
 To je mistična molitva

709
00:34:03,120 --> 00:34:05,100
 da od dragi Boga

710
00:34:05,100 --> 00:34:06,020
 bi svi došli do toga,

711
00:34:06,020 --> 00:34:07,180
 ali redovito mali broj

712
00:34:07,180 --> 00:34:08,020
 do toga dolazi.

713
00:34:08,020 --> 00:34:08,520
 E sada,

714
00:34:08,520 --> 00:34:10,220
 konkretno to znači ovo.

715
00:34:10,220 --> 00:34:13,000
 Treba u početku duhovnog života

716
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:15,140
 usvojiti jednu molitvenu metodu.

717
00:34:15,140 --> 00:34:16,520
 Najko je reći,

718
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:17,640
 pa molit ću se,

719
00:34:17,640 --> 00:34:18,880
 kaj idem spavat,

720
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:19,880
 učinit ću znak križa

721
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:21,120
 i anđelu Čuvaru.

722
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:23,140
 To je kao kad bi ja rekao

723
00:34:23,140 --> 00:34:23,860
 čega živiš,

724
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:25,440
 kaže, uzmam tri zličice mlijeka

725
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,020
 svaki dan.

726
00:34:26,020 --> 00:34:27,820
 Pa neće baš dugo živjeti.

727
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:29,840
 Treba se dobro hraniti.

728
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,100
 I naš duh je potreban

729
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:31,860
 dobre hrane.

730
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:34,600
 Molitva je hrana duše,

731
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:36,600
 a to znači da je jako važno

732
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:37,480
 u početku duhovnog života

733
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:39,080
 osvojiti jednu molitvenu metodu.

734
00:34:39,080 --> 00:34:40,600
 Postoji razne molitvene metode.

735
00:34:40,600 --> 00:34:43,280
 Ja redovito studentima teologije

736
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:45,180
 sogerira nešto što je crkva

737
00:34:45,180 --> 00:34:46,760
 iznijedila stoljećima,

738
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:48,260
 stoljećima duhovnog rasta

739
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:49,880
 unutar monaške duhovnosti,

740
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,120
 a ta se metoda zove

741
00:34:51,120 --> 00:34:52,600
 lekcijo divina.

742
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:54,660
 A to znači molitveni sustreć

743
00:34:54,660 --> 00:34:55,680
 sa riječom Božijom.

744
00:34:55,680 --> 00:34:57,020
 Da svaki dan

745
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:58,700
 otvaran svetopismo,

746
00:34:58,700 --> 00:35:00,720
 najbolje možda evanđelje od dana,

747
00:35:00,720 --> 00:35:03,080
 da na tom Božijom riječu

748
00:35:03,080 --> 00:35:04,100
 koja je živa,

749
00:35:04,100 --> 00:35:05,220
 koja je djelotvorna,

750
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:05,400
 kaže,

751
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:06,260
 potrebno se hebrajima,

752
00:35:06,260 --> 00:35:07,920
 oštrija od vosijekog mača,

753
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:09,340
 sila za unašnu utrinu,

754
00:35:09,340 --> 00:35:10,720
 ona me rasvjetljava,

755
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:12,760
 ona mi otkriva mene meni,

756
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:14,580
 otkriva mi Božji pogled na mene,

757
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:16,940
 i onda tom riječu osvjetljena,

758
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:18,700
 ona mi postaje program moga života,

759
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:20,280
 postaje hrana moga življenja.

760
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:22,480
 To je možda najbolja metoda,

761
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:24,960
 svakako za vjeru učitelje,

762
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:26,180
 za studenti teologije,

763
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:27,620
 za intelektualce,

764
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:31,240
 možda za ljude koji nemaju,

765
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:31,620
 možda,

766
00:35:31,620 --> 00:35:33,460
 sklonost čitanju,

767
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:34,900
 ili ovoj vrstni molitve,

768
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:37,120
 molitva krunice je jako dobra,

769
00:35:37,220 --> 00:35:39,980
 ali mora bi povezana sa razmatranjem.

770
00:35:39,980 --> 00:35:41,240
 Moram se,

771
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:42,200
 evo,

772
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:44,680
 naučiti,

773
00:35:44,680 --> 00:35:46,600
 moram učiniti dodatan napor,

774
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:49,020
 da svoj duh usmjeri prema otajstvima

775
00:35:49,020 --> 00:35:50,280
 gospodina Isusa Krista,

776
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,080
 njegova života,

777
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:53,320
 i onda u Marijinoj školi

778
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:55,280
 ja otkrivam ljepotu

779
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:56,640
 i dubine Kristova otajstva,

780
00:35:56,640 --> 00:35:57,740
 ljepotu Kristova lica,

781
00:35:57,740 --> 00:36:00,540
 i tako u meni onda raste duhovni život.

782
00:36:01,240 --> 00:36:01,980
 Dragi domladene,

783
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,920
 hvala vam što ste gostovali danas,

784
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:05,000
 što ste bili s nama.

785
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,820
 Neka nam ovo svima bude poticaj

786
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:08,380
 za bogatiji duhovni život.

787
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:10,000
 Vama, dragi gledatelji,

788
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,280
 hvala puno na gledanju.

789
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:13,240
 Pozivamo vas da budete s nama

790
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,440
 i u idućinem misijama.

791
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:15,260
 Pratite nas.

792
00:36:15,260 --> 00:36:16,340
 Boži blagoslov.

793
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:32,700
 Hvala vam što ste.

